            {
                "name": "Very",
                "url": "/topics/very"
            },
            {
                "name": "Mass",
                "url": "/topics/mass"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/andrea_m_ghez_664486",
        "quote": "One of the key differences between galaxies with super massive black holes is whether or not the black holes are lit up, because they are basically bingeing on a lot of material in its surroundings.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Andrea M. Ghez",
            "url": "/quotes/andrea_m_ghez_664486"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Black",
                "url": "/topics/black"
            },
            {
                "name": "Differences",
                "url": "/topics/differences"
            },
            {
                "name": "Galaxies",
                "url": "/topics/galaxies"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/andrea_m_ghez_664487",
        "quote": "One of the big mysteries about the black hole at the center of the galaxy is, 'Why don't we see emission from matter falling onto the black hole, or, rather, the black hole eating up its surroundings?'",
        "author": {
            "name": "Andrea M. Ghez",
            "url": "/quotes/andrea_m_ghez_664487"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Falling",
                "url": "/topics/falling"
            },
            {
                "name": "Big",
                "url": "/topics/big"
            },
            {
                "name": "Rather",
                "url": "/topics/rather"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/andrea_m_ghez_664488",
        "quote": "Proof of the black hole is a tremendous amount of mass inside a very small volume. There's 4 million times the mass of our sun within a region that's comparable to the size of our solar system.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Andrea M. Ghez",
            "url": "/quotes/andrea_m_ghez_664488"
        },
        "topics": [
